Package: reclink
Title: Record Linkage of Brazilian Names
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("User", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "user@example.com")
Description: Tools for probabilistic record linkage of Brazilian names,
    using Jaro-Winkler similarity, name frequency weighting from IBGE data,
    and gender-aware surname matching.
